1.1.	Description of enhancement
What is the business scenario?  Describe what the enhancement will do, why is it needed, who the intended users are, and the overall goal.

Item category ZQPC is defaulted to every ZQP system component. Item category ZQPC is only valid for components being issued from normal inventory stock. The user can manually change the item category before saving.
This enhancement will automate item category determination update in ECC order for a line item with Item category ZQPC and Plant 1018 to ZKQP prior to order save. This change supports the new QP Systems sales BOM process, ensuring consigned components are correctly identified, availability checks are bypassed, and consignment handling is applied automatically. 
The Enhancement will be applicable for Plants and Item Categories maintained in ZUPRGMVAR Table.
