EDD13337_ZQP_PLANTS	1018 (Non EMEA Plant Entries)	
EDD13337_ZQP_ITEMCAT_CHG_EMEA	Item category to fetch from order (EMEA Entry)	Item category to be updated in order (EMEA Entry)
EDD13337_ZQP_PLANTS_EMEA	EMEA Plant to check for EMEA Variant	

 

Obtain the ECC Plant numbers VBAP - WERKS
b)	Proceed only if the above data is maintained in the ZUPRGMVAR table.
c)	Using suitable User exit/BADI obtain the items, Plant and the partners for the order.

